# Game server's signing keypair (base58 encoded secret key, 32 or 64 bytes)
# Generate: solana-keygen new --outfile game-authority.json
# Then:     python3 -c "import json,base58; print(base58.b58encode(bytes(json.load(open('game-authority.json')))).decode())"
# The PUBLIC KEY from this keypair must be set as NEXT_PUBLIC_GAME_AUTHORITY_PUBKEY in the web app.
